{"tid":523903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭真係幾好野！","createTime":"2018-01-09T04:51:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T18:08:02.000Z","uid":28195,"like":784,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":74,"replies":[{"pid":"7f12ef2832a6021b751129c2a625f6ea084344b1","tid":523903,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/09/125008_316498ecbd1055e6082cdab6a50c94da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F09%2F125008_316498ecbd1055e6082cdab6a50c94da.png&h=d0c4c261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特首︰鄭若驊住宅涉僭建事件任命後才發生 不存在隱瞞</span></span><br />\n　2018-01-09 10:01<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都講得出口，同精英主議論同一個level"},{"pid":"8226fec28057491445fb2e5186ae6b4af306530e","tid":523903,"uid":28195,"like":33,"dislike":4,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:52:45.000Z","msg":"source: <a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5a542293e60383352df9fbd5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5a542293e60383352df9fbd5%2F&d=xX77hroXdMzR4jOVmCMNZTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=74551f63\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5a542293e60383352df9fbd5/</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，律政司司長鄭若驊住宅涉嫌僭建事件，是在一月五日下午在中央任命後才發生，鄭若驊當天下午已向她報告，不存在隱瞞，希望外界給予她空間處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥稱：「可能她是警覺性不足，去接受我邀請任命做律政司司長的政治敏感度亦不太足夠，未能將她物業內懷疑僭建的事先將其釐清。無論如何，她承諾這件事釐清後，她會馬上交代以及盡快改正。鄭若驊女士仍然是我心目中，一位非常理想擔任律政司司長的人選。正如這兩日有法律界人士都說，今日要放棄非常成功的私人執業，進入所謂『熱廚房』擔任律政司司長，都是一個作出犧牲的決定。我也可以跟大家說過去一段時間的組班過程，真的非常困難。」"},{"pid":"656a221cd0295baa581b91d68b28ba88861f1a6a","tid":523903,"uid":36238,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T04:52:51.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb4f64c320b98d07c9fd62a1a628d25af8267b7","tid":523903,"uid":66496,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":1,"